# Team Rules (Override Example)

This is an **example rules file** for documenting team conventions. It is ignored by default because it ends in `.example`.

## Example Rules

- **Requirement sources**: Only Jira Stories and Features are valid sources.
- **Do not analyze**: Bugs and Epics (bugs go to “Concerns / Known Bugs” only).
- **Anti-hallucination**: Never invent API/DB details; mark as pending.
- **Excel exports**: Always include the Jira key in the output folder name under `outputs/<Project>/runs/`.

## How to enable

Copy to `overrides/rules/team_rules.md` (remove `.example`) if you want AIRA to treat it as an active rule artifact.

